<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.4.4">
<l>kuṉṟeṭut tānirai kātta pirāṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">kōvala ṉāykkuḻa lūti yūti</l>
<l>kaṉṟukaḷ mēyttu(t)taṉ tōḻa rōṭu</l>
<l rend="indent">kalantuṭaṉ varuvāṉait teruvil kaṇ</l>
<l>ṭeṉṟumi vaṉaiyop pārai naṅkāy</l>
<l rend="indent">kaṇṭaṟi yēṉēṭi vantu kāṇā</l>
<l>yoṉṟumnil lāvaḷai kaḻaṉṟu tuki</l>
<l rend="indent">lēntiḷa mulaiyumeṉ vacamal lavē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Girls! Come and see the lord who protected the cow herd</l>
<l rend="indent">by raising a mountian as a herder,</l>
<l>Seeing him coming in the street playing [his] flute</l>
<l rend="indent">along with his friends after grazing the claves,</l>
<l>Ladies, I know I have never seen anyone like him.</l>
<l>[My] bangles slip off, not even one staying put,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] even [my] sari[-clad] ample young breasts are not in my control.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
